\c 2
\s Jona anonyengetera ari mukati mehove
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Jona akanyengetera kuna Jehovha Mwari wake ari mudumbu rehove.
\v 2 Akati, Ndakadana kuna Jehovha ndiri munhamo yangu, Akandipindura; Ndakadana ndiri mudumbu reSheori, imwi mukanzwa izwi rangu.
\p
\v 3 nekuti makandikandira makadzika, mukati momwoyo wegungwa, Mvura zhinji yakanga yandikomberedza; Mafungu enyu namapoporodzi enyu akapfuura napamusoro pangu.
\p
\v 4 Ndikati, Ndarashwa, hamuchandioni; Asi ndicharingirazve kuTemberi yenyu tsvene.
\p
\v 5 Mvura zhinji yakandikomberedza, kusvikira kumweya wangu; Pakadzika pakanga pandipoteredza; Maharanga akanga amonera musoro wangu.
\p
\v 6 Ndakaburukira kumavambiso amakomo; Nyika, zvipfigiso zvayo zvakandipfigiramo nokusingaperi; kunyange zvakadaro makabudisa upenyu hwangu pagomba, imi, Jehovha Mwari wangu.
\v 7 Mweya wangu wakati uchiziya mukati mangu, ndikarangarira Jehovha; Munyengetero wangu ukapinda kwamuri, mutemberi yenyu tsvene.
\v 8 Vanorangarira zvisina maturo zvenhema Vanorasha nyasha yavo.
\p
\v 9 Asi ndichakubayirai nenzwi rokuvonga; Ndicharipa zvandapika. Ruponeso runobva kuna Jehovha.
\v 10 Jehovha akataura nehove, ikandorutsira Jona panyika yakaoma.
